725134f-a.title: Queens: 24th Avenue - 38th Street
725134f-a.text:
24th Avenue, at 38th Street, showing two views of demolition operations. The buildings are being razed to make way for the construction of Grand Central Parkway. View 1 shows the N.W. corner of the intersection, and view 2 the remains of a four-story apartment house at the S.E. corner.
P. L. Sperr  September 20, 1934
NO REPRODUCTIONS  Views 1,2
